name: Inzektor Centipede
effectText: Once per turn: You can equip 1 "Inzektor" monster from your hand or GY to this card. If an Equip Card(s) is sent to your GY while equipped to this card (except during the Damage Step): You can add 1 "Inzektor" card from your Deck to your hand. While this card is equipped to a monster, that monster's Level is increased by 3.
